node.accessibility_caption: Photo by HoodClips on September 12, 2021. May be an image of 3 people and text that says 'Conor McGregor is seen trying to fight Machine Gun Kelly after he denied to take a picture with him at the VMA's'.

node.text:
According to sources, #MGK pushed #ConorMcGregor who was asking for a photo, causing him to spill his drink at the #VMA's. Conor then picked up the cup and threw it at MGK ensuing a physical altercation. 

Swipe to see some of internet’s best reactions! 👉
